":"It was not the ferry watcher who oiled the gears.","id":"c3","operands":[{"cat":"vessel","value":"ferry"},{"cat":"chore","value":"gears"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"4 hours was not the one who logged the tug.","id":"c4","operands":[{"cat":"watch","value":"watch4"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"tug"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"Hideo trimmed the wick.","id":"c5","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"hideo"},{"cat":"chore","value":"wick"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"It was the tea drinker who stood watch for 10 hours.","id":"c6","operands":[{"cat":"flask","value":"tea"},{"cat":"watch","value":"watch10"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"The one who polished the lens was the tea drinker.","id":"c7","operands":[{"cat":"flask","value":"tea"},{"cat":"chore","value":"lens"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"The one who stood watch for 4 hours was the ginger-soda drinker.","id":"c8","operands":[{"cat":"flask","value":"soda"},{"cat":"watch","value":"watch4"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"Marina was not the one who kept warm with the ginger soda.","id":"c9","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"marina"},{"cat":"flask","value":"soda"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"Saoirse was down to Hot juice or Coffee, and only one was right.","id":"c10","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"saoirse"},{"cat":"flask","value":"juice"},{"cat":"flask","value":"coffee"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneOf","type":"oneOf"},{"clueText":"It was not 12 hours who logged the sloop.","id":"c11","operands":[{"cat":"watch","value":"watch12"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"sloop"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"Of Nils and Saoirse, one logged the cutter and the other logged the schooner.","id":"c12","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"nils"},{"cat":"keeper","value":"saoirse"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"cutter"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"schooner"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneEachOf","type":"oneEachOf"},{"clueText":"the coffee drinker stood watch for 12 hours.","id":"c13","operands":[{"cat":"flask","value":"coffee"},{"cat":"watch","value":"watch12"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"6 hours logged the schooner.","id":"c14","operands":[{"cat":"watch","value":"watch6"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"schooner"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"Of Hideo and Cormac, one logged the sloop and the other logged the trawler.","id":"c15","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"hideo"},{"cat":"keeper","value":"cormac"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"sloop"},{"cat":"vessel","value":"trawler"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneEachOf","type":"oneEachOf"},{"clueText":"Of Hideo and Saoirse, one trimmed the wick and the other logged the tides.","id":"c16","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"hideo"},{"cat":"keeper","value":"saoirse"},{"cat":"chore","value":"wick"},{"cat":"chore","value":"tides"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneEachOf","type":"oneEachOf"},{"clueText":"Marina was down to Wind the clock or Polish the lens, and only one was right.","id":"c17","operands":[{"cat":"keeper","value":"marina"},{"cat":"chore","value":"clock"},{"cat":"chore","value":"lens"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneOf","type":"oneOf"}],"entities":["e0","e1","e2","e3","e4","e5"],"hintTrace":[{"forces":{"cat":"flask","entity":"e3","value":"coffee"},"fromClues":["c10","c13"]},{"forces":{"cat":"flask","entity":"e4","value":"tea"},"fromClues":["c2","c6","c7"]},{"forces":{"cat":"flask","entity":"e5","value":"juice"},"fromClues":["c10"]},{"forces":{"cat":"flask","entity":"e2","value":"soda"},"fromClues":["c8","c9"]},{"forces":{"cat":"flask","entity":"e1","value":"water"},"fromClues":["c2"]},{"forces":{"cat":"flask","entity":"e0","value":"milk"},"fromClues":["c1"]},{"forces":{"cat":"watch","entity":"e1","value":"watch8"},"fromClues":["c1"]},{"forces":{"cat":"watch","entity":"e0","value"