d the lamp turns steady overhead as six keepers trade off through the long night, and Chief Mara sorts out whose night was whose after a gust through the door knocked the logbook to the floor. Each keeper has a different flask, watch, vessel and chore. Using the clues, match every keeper to their flask, watch, vessel and chore.","subjectNoun":"keeper","templateRev":1,"tier":"expert","variant":1}
